\((\frac{{@Goats_angle@}}{360})\times {@Total_farm_animals@}  - (\frac{{@Sheeps_angle@}}{360})\times {@Total_farm_animals@} \)

which is equal \({@tans3@}\)
</p></li>
<li><p>
There are {@tans4@} more Turkeys than Ducks are on the farm

